            <a href="https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/768803/GAR_Instructions_July_2018-3-1-19.pdf">
              General aviation report guidance(GAR)
            </a>
					</li>
					<li>
            <a href="https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/380032/border_force_expectations_of_airfiield_operators.pdf">
              Border Force expectations of airfield operators
            </a>
					</li>
					<li>
            <a href="https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/768803/GAR_Instructions_July_2018-3-1-19.pdf">
              Check if you need to submit a GAR
            </a>
					</li>
					<li>
            <a href="https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/408958/6_478_Aviation_poster.pdf">
              Emergency (GAR) telephone line
            </a>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</nav>
		</aside>

	</div>
</div>
